==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Opener
<hw>O"pen*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, opens.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧True <xex>opener</xex> of my
eyes.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>A bottle opener or a
can opener; <as>as, you need an <ex>opener</ex> to get the cap
off</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Open-eyed</ent>⟦br⟧
